Interface DocumentGrammarListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DocumentGrammarBaseListener

    public interface DocumentGrammarListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by DocumentGrammarParser.
